Police have released disturbing images of an arsonist pouring inflammable liquid through the letterbox of an elderly couple and then setting the front door ablaze as they slept.

The attacker can be seen calmly bending down as he pours the liquid, believed to be lighter fluid, through the letterbox while trying to hide beneath a large umbrella.

He then slips to the ground on the pathway in the front garden as he makes his getaway from the house in Wallington, Surrey.

